snippet.title: CinemaTyler
snippet.description:
"When people ask me if I went to film school I tell them 'no, I went to films.'" - Quentin Tarantino

Here at CinemaTyler, we take an in-depth look into the construction of some of cinema’s greatest movies. This channel is devoted to understanding filmmaking through watching, researching, and analyzing movies and film history.
